# 🔍 Forensic 360 - Digital Investigation Platform  

Forensic 360 is an advanced digital forensic investigation tool built using **FastAPI (Backend), Firebase (Database), and React (Frontend)**. This platform enables secure forensic data analysis, evidence management, and reporting.  

## 🚀 Project Overview  
Forensic 360 aims to streamline digital forensic investigations by providing a secure, scalable, and efficient solution for evidence collection, analysis, and reporting.  

## 🛠️ Tech Stack  
- **Backend**: FastAPI (Python)  
- **Database**: Firebase Firestore & Firebase Storage  
- **Frontend**: React (JavaScript)  
- **Authentication**: Firebase Auth  
- **Hosting**: Firebase Hosting / Vercel  

---

## 📅 Roadmap  

### 📌 **Phase 1: Project Setup (Day 1-2)**  
✅ Create GitHub Repository  
✅ Setup FastAPI Project  
✅ Setup Firebase & Firestore  
✅ Initialize React Frontend  

### 📌 **Phase 2: Backend Development (Day 3-10)**  
- [ ] Implement Firebase Authentication in FastAPI  
- [ ] Develop API endpoints for:  
  - User Authentication (Signup/Login)  
  - Upload & Retrieve Forensic Data  
  - Evidence Analysis & Report Generation  
- [ ] Connect FastAPI with Firebase Firestore & Storage  

### 📌 **Phase 3: Frontend Development (Day 11-20)**  
- [ ] Implement Firebase Auth in React  
- [ ] Create UI for:  
  - User Authentication  
  - Dashboard (Upload & View Forensic Evidence)  
  - Report Generation  
- [ ] Integrate FastAPI APIs with React  

### 📌 **Phase 4: Testing & Deployment (Day 21-27)**  
- [ ] End-to-End Testing  
- [ ] Optimize Performance & Fix Bugs  
- [ ] Deploy Backend & Frontend (Firebase / Vercel)  

### 📌 **Phase 5: Final Touches & Presentation (Day 28-30)**  
- [ ] Polish UI & Improve UX  
- [ ] Prepare Demo & Documentation  
- [ ] Submit Project for Final Evaluation  

---

## 🎯 Features (MVP)  
✅ **User Authentication** (Firebase Auth)  
✅ **Upload Forensic Data** (Images, Videos, Documents)  
✅ **Secure Storage & Retrieval** (Firebase Firestore)  
✅ **Automated Evidence Processing**  
✅ **Report Generation & Visualization**  

